{"id": 456, "genre": 1000, "title": "那么，我们做了个美言APP的试用版本", "description": "“考虑开发一款美言APP？你输入一句很普通的话，比如“我爱你”，然后选择美言，APP会自动帮你调整错字语气标点韵脚，这是基本功能。还可以添加各种滤镜…”——马伯庸", "record_count": 2864, "comment_count": 17, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160703130109gaX4z0vbqlHM2EGe.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-07-31T01:00:24Z", "questions": [{"id": 357, "title": "那么，我们做了个美言APP的试用版本", "content": "像美图一样美化语言，你想要哪种说话风格？", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 6462, "content": "用鲁迅滤镜表述“我朋友太抠”", "image": "img/option/option/20160702182800RGK5XF7rJP8u4hgV.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 6464, "content": "用琼瑶滤镜表述“前女友去死”", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193146J2sX48CT1LvfnptW.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 6466, "content": "用张嘉佳滤镜表述“想吃夜宵”", "image": "img/option/option/20160703125937Og07iornzXd9y5Fa.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 6469, "content": "用大咕咕咕鸡滤镜表述纠结外卖吃什么的心情", "image": "img/option/option/201606071931463FaN6sloUD0pEf4X.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 6470, "content": "用苹果广告滤镜教你给你妈送礼", "image": "img/option/option/201606071931460c1RT4HBvdOtSQ8s.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 6472, "content": "日漫主题包表述“别抢我东西吃”", "image": "img/option/option/201607031259373UElVWNdcbe8ra7p.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 6473, "content": "英译主题包表述“我说的没错吧”", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193146uE0jaJo3KDZmf9iM.jpeg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}